      required in newer gnome shell versions), and replaces with newer selectors/styling
      (modifying to match Arc styling where necessary)
    * Integrates styling from the default gnome shell theme into the Arc shell theme.
      Because the user shell theme (Arc in this case) is "overlaid" over the default shell
      theme, this is styling that was being "pulled in" anyway.
